    !.
calcH(T,X,Y):-
    check(T,V), X1 is X+V, T1 is T+1, calcH(T1,X1,Y).
check(T,V):-
    tp(T,A,B),gtp(T,C,D), A=C, B=D, V is 0,1.
check(_,1):-
    !.
